Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a hole in the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can see why it's a sacred mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What a magnificent sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, I'll have some buckwheat noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it. Two orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And some sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, buddy.
